W

Word - Class in implementations
The Word class represent the implementation of storing the information of words found as objects along with its number of appearances across files with line numbers.
Word(String, int, String) - Constructor for class implementations.Word
Constructs a Word object, constructing it with the given word, its line number, and the file name where it was found.
WordTracker - Class in implementations
The WordTracker class is the implementation for tracking words from the extracted text file, storing them in a Binary Search Tree as objects within each node, and tracking their appearances across files and line numbers.
WordTracker(String, PrintStream) - Constructor for class implementations.WordTracker
The constructor of a WordTracker take the passed in input text file and optional output stream.
